name: adb-shell
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "adb-shell" %}
{% set version = "0.4.3" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/adb_shell-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 1cc7847cbd901b1419fe48664bffbe2481b4fa1bba03fe3074abd97228535a82

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - cryptography
    - pyasn1
    - python >=3.6
    - rsa

test:
  imports:
    - adb_shell
    - adb_shell.auth
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/JeffLIrion/adb_shell
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_family: Apache
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: A Python implementation of ADB with shell and FileSync functionality.
  description: |
    This Python package implements ADB shell and FileSync functionality. 
    It originated from python-adb.
  doc_url: https://adb-shell.readthedocs.io/
  dev_url: https://github.com/JeffLIrion/adb_shell

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jan-janssen
